title: Pineapple cake
description:
About Product:-

The outer skin of traditional pineapple cake is made of lard, and the filling is mostly made of pineapple mixed with winter melon.Â In recent years, many merchants have used pure pineapple to make fillings. Although its taste is not as dense and soft as the winter melon filling, the unique and rich fruity flavor with such sweet and sour taste of pure pineapple filling is incomparable with winter melon filling.
